name: The Trees and The Life #004-Cikole
description:
"Let's hang on the pine trees" my friends said, using a hammock if you wonder. We lit the woods, grilled some food. Everybody loves around the pine forest, its breeze, its smell, its aura, its soothe you. The more you look up at night, the pines seem dancing on a starry night while listening to our laughing.

The Trees and The Life is a 10-Photo-Based-NFT Collection made by Danar Tri Atmojo. As the first-ever collection made, Danar dedicated these NFT's to mother nature as we move towards the new era of digitalization using Tezos blockchain as #CleanNFTs.
